---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for TheEduAssist.">

        <section class="py-20 bg-white px-4">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
                <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 mb-8">
                    <p class="text-yellow-800 font-medium">Disclaimer: This page is a general placeholder and should be reviewed by a legal professional before launch.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-600">
                    <p>At TheEduAssist, your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy document outlines the types of personal information received and collected by TheEduAssist and how it is used.</p>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Information Collection</h2>
                    <p>We only collect information about you if we have a reason to do so, such as providing our services, communicating with you, or making our services better.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

</Layout>
